      "asbval:evidence_quote": "We engineered a machine learning approach, MSHub, to enable auto-deconvolution of gas chromatography-mass spectrometry (GC-MS) data. We then designed workflows to enable the community to store, process, share, annotate, compare and perform molecular networking of GC-MS data within the Global Natural Product Social (GNPS) Molecular Networking analysis platform.",
      "asbval:note": "Research question directly supported by abstract and introduction describing MSHub's purpose for auto-deconvolution and molecular networking.",
