      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Convert raw gas chromatography\u2013mass spectrometry (GC-MS) data into standardized, deconvolved mass spectra suitable for downstream molecular networking and spectral library matching. This skill resolves overlapping peaks in complex chromatographic mixtures and exports individual c",
