      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The source code of the MSHub software, including low- and high resolution data processing versions is available online at Github (version used in GNPS) (https://github.com/CCMS-UCSD/GNPS_Workflows/tree/master/mshub-gc/tools/mshub-gc/proc) and at BitBucket (standalone version in MSHub developers' repository, both high and low resolution: https://bitbucket.org/iAnalytica/mshub_process/src/master/). Scripts used to parse, filter, organize data and generate the plots in the manuscript are available online at Github (https://github.com/bittremieux/GNPS_GC_fig).",
      "asbval:note": "Paper provides multiple GitHub repositories for MSHub code. The card's URL (https://github.com/bittremieux/GNPS_GC) appears to be a supporting repository for figure generation scripts, not the primary MSHub source code. Primary MSHub source is at https://github.com/CCMS-UCSD/GNPS_Workflows/tree/master/mshub-gc/tools/mshub-gc/proc. The card's URL is a valid but secondary repository.",
