    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/molecular-network-graph-parsing/000",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "GNPS has now expanded to include GC-MS-specific molecular networking. One of the developments that enabled finding structural relationships within mass spectrometry data is spectral alignment, which forms the basis for molecular networking.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms GNPS performs GC-MS molecular networking and produces network outputs, but does not explicitly describe parsing/validating GraphML or JSON output files. The paper focuses on GNPS workflow execution and network visualization, not on downstream parsing of network file formats. The specific task of 'parsing and validating' network output files in GraphML/JSON format is not documented in the passages.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1038-s41587-020-0700-3",
